@startuml
actor Customer
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "customer-service" as CustomerService
database "MySQL Customer DB" as CustomerDB

Customer -> Gateway: GET /api/customers/cart/summary/
Gateway -> CustomerService: GET /customers/cart/summary/
CustomerService -> CustomerService: Validate JWT customer
CustomerService -> CustomerDB: Load cart and cart_items
CustomerDB --> CustomerService: Cart data
CustomerService -> CustomerService: Calculate total amount
CustomerService --> Gateway: Summary response
Gateway --> Customer: Cart summary
@enduml
